    "description": "<strong>《Isle of Siptah》是开放世界生存游戏《Conan Exiles》的大型扩展，内含一片广阔的岛屿地区供你探索，其中有身形巨大且天性凶恶的生物，更有全新建筑材料和一整套全新玩法。在全新地下城中与远古种族战斗。在由纯粹混沌构成的风暴中，击败诞生于此的恶魔怪物。占领浪潮，在其中捕捉从大陆地区召唤来的强大仆役。</strong><br><br>在一场船难后，你孤身来到了这座岛。你的身后仅剩下船骸碎片，你要自己手工制作生存用品。先是简单的营地和粗制的石器，假以时日，则是堡垒和用硬钢或黑曜石铸造的野蛮大剑。<br><br>你的视线转向岛屿的中心，看到了一座暗色高塔与周围的地貌格格不入。绕着它旋转的猛烈风暴仿佛在集聚力量，其中潜藏着不可言说的恐怖之物。不过最危险的敌人可能是岛上的其他求生者——毕竟资源稀少，生存竞争野蛮残酷。     <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/6269dbd4619f7bbffab75aabbd445f16.poster.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/6269dbd4619f7bbffab75aabbd445f16.webm?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/6269dbd4619f7bbffab75aabbd445f16.mp4?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在广阔的西普塔岛上开始全新旅程。这里有许多地方等你来探索：遍布沉船残骸的阳光海滩，茂密高大的红木森林，散布着古老亚切隆遗迹的开阔山谷，安置移民的斯泰吉亚殖民地，海盗肆虐的不详营地，以及岛中心充满噩兆的西普塔高塔。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/c438d3524e764320a186f6054e31e760.poster.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/c438d3524e764320a186f6054e31e760.webm?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/c438d3524e764320a186f6054e31e760.mp4?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索被遗忘已久的暗窖，发掘其中遥远过去的远古种族留下的痕迹。找到隐藏的大厅，解决古老的谜题，并杀死其中的邪魔恶鬼。掠夺珍贵宝藏，驾驭远古种族的力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/4f59182ed90d6e905ddf801e830dc0f6.poster.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/4f59182ed90d6e905ddf801e830dc0f6.webm?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/4f59182ed90d6e905ddf801e830dc0f6.mp4?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一场大风暴围绕在岛中心的黑塔周围。它受恶毒魔力所驱动，不断从外域虚空带来恐怖的怪兽，向任何胆敢踏入的人发动攻击。击败这些怪兽，获取一种全新的关键资源和独特奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/28ef137de6765ef9fda32151b44b5bcc.poster.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/28ef137de6765ef9fda32151b44b5bcc.webm?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/28ef137de6765ef9fda32151b44b5bcc.mp4?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>古神奈亚拉托提普的禁忌魔法从西普塔高塔中发出，生成强大的浪潮。其他世界的人类和生物被这些神秘的浪潮传送至这里。抓紧时间捕获他们。让其他玩家有时间组建军队，你就只能甘拜下风。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/36dfa9801fd24f2637f298bd1cd3a662.poster.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/36dfa9801fd24f2637f298bd1cd3a662.webm?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/36dfa9801fd24f2637f298bd1cd3a662.mp4?t=1622114550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>驾驭凶猛的犀牛冲进战场，屠戮敌人！从小型房屋到大城市，可选用两种新型建材：浸水船骸的打捞物建材以及古老雄伟的风暴玻璃。寻找并装备强大的物品，例如新的护甲套装、工具和武器。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206200/extras/63d4f30344de269958e740228538a4c0.avif?t=1622114550\" width=616 height=1296 /></span>",
